ftpd.library/RemoveSnoopHook                       ftpd.library/RemoveSnoopHook
  NAME
	RemoveSnoopHook - remove an input/output monitoring hook.

  SYNOPSIS
	RemoveSnoopHook( hook, ftp );
	                  A0   A1

	void RemoveSnoopHook( struct Hook *hook, struct FTPData *ftp );

  FUNCTION
	This removes a previously added snoop hook. It is permissable to call it
	with ftp being NULL - in this case this hook is removed from every ftp
	that is using it.

  INPUTS
	hook - callback hook

	ftp - connection remove hook from
